title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Convention Center on 1986-02-08
description:
Set 1

Iko Iko
Little Red Rooster
Peggy-O
Beat It On Down The Line

Drums
Space

Sugar Magnolia

Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
